    {
      "id": "fall-of-the-old-keep",
      "title": "Fall of the Old Keep",
      "type": "event",
      "world": "astrath-deeprealm",
      "visibility": "player",
      "canon": "canon",
      "aliases": [],
      "tags": [
        "calamity",
        "ruins"
      ],
      "summary": "The Old Keep falls in a single night to a shadow that came down from the high passes.",
      "images": [],
      "body": "\r\nOn the third night of Longnight, 612 AS, the watchfires of the [[The Old Keep|Old Keep]]\r\nwent dark. Riders from [[Raven's Vale]] found the gates open and the courtyards\r\nempty by morning. Whatever passed that night left no bodies, only frost.\r\n\r\nThe keep has stood abandoned ever since.\r\n",
      "bodyHtml": "<p>On the third night of Longnight, 612 AS, the watchfires of the <span class=\"atlas-unresolved\">Old Keep</span>\nwent dark. Riders from <span class=\"atlas-unresolved\">Raven's Vale</span> found the gates open and the courtyards\nempty by morning. Whatever passed that night left no bodies, only frost.</p>\n<p>The keep has stood abandoned ever since.</p>\n",
