    {
      "id": "the-sundering",
      "title": "The Sundering",
      "type": "event",
      "world": "astrath-deeprealm",
      "visibility": "player",
      "canon": "canon",
      "aliases": [],
      "tags": [
        "cataclysm",
        "founding"
      ],
      "summary": "The cataclysm that split the old continent and ended the Third Age. The new calendar reckons years from the day the sky cracked.",
      "images": [],
      "body": "\r\nWhen the Twin Moons collided in the night sky, the firmament tore and the seas\r\nboiled. Half of the old continent slid beneath the waves; what remained\r\nbecame the Astrath Deeprealm. Survivors founded the great cities of\r\n[[Thornhold]] and [[Sunhaven]] in the years that followed.\r\n\r\nThis event marks year **0** of the *After Sundering* calendar.\r\n",
      "bodyHtml": "<p>When the Twin Moons collided in the night sky, the firmament tore and the seas\nboiled. Half of the old continent slid beneath the waves; what remained\nbecame the Astrath Deeprealm. Survivors founded the great cities of\n<span class=\"atlas-unresolved\">Thornhold</span> and <span class=\"atlas-unresolved\">Sunhaven</span> in the years that followed.</p>\n<p>This event marks year <strong>0</strong> of the <em>After Sundering</em> calendar.</p>\n",
